original_title: Nøtteknekkeren - ballett i to akter fra Den Norske Opera & Ballett
overview: The Nutcracker is about a young girl who receives a nutcracker as a gift from a puppeteer. That same night, she dreams of a world where the nutcracker is alive, and where they have to fight a rat king who is going to take them.
title: Nøtteknekkeren - ballett i to akter fra Den Norske Opera & Ballett
